{
  "TopicId": 8,
  "Title": "Balanced Parentheses",
  "Description": "Given a string of brackets, return `true` if balanced, `false` otherwise. Valid pairs: `()` `[]` `{}`\n\n**Input:** single line string.\n\n**Example:**\n- Input: `({[]})`\n- Output: `true`\n\n**Constraints:**\n- 0 <= length <= 1,000,000\n- Expected complexity: O(n)",
  "Difficulty": 2,
  "TimeLimitMs": 3000,
  "MemoryLimitKb": 131072,
